name: 鼠鼠我啊
description: 当 “鼠鼠我啊” 从一句自嘲的网络热梗，演变为超千万人共鸣的情绪出口，它早已超越简单的表情包文化，成为 Z 世代直面生活、彼此慰藉的精神图腾。鼠鼠我啊，要做世界上第一个被央妈发送 到太空的迷因币。 When "Me, the Mouse" evolved from a self-deprecating internet meme into an emotional outlet resonating with over ten million people, it has long transcended simple emoji culture, becoming a spiritual totem for Generation Z to face life and comfort each other. Me, the Mouse, wants to be the world's first meme coin sent into space by the central bank.
